# ========== 1. 忽略不需要的独立项目文件夹 ==========
CplusAdvanced/
CplusBasic/
CplusCore/
RoomReservation/
SpeechContest/
StaffManagement/

# ========== 2. Visual Studio 生成的临时/配置文件（每台电脑不一样，必须忽略） ==========
.vs/
*.suo
*.user
*.vcxproj.user
*.vcproj.*.user
*.sdf
*.opensdf
*.cache
*.log
*.lastbuildstate

# ========== 3. 编译生成的目录（所有层级的Debug/Release/x64，嵌套目录也能匹配） ==========
Debug/
Release/
x64/
x86/
ipch/

# ========== 4. 编译生成的二进制/中间文件 ==========
*.exe
*.dll
*.pdb
*.ilk
*.obj
*.tlog
*.tlh
*.tli
*.pch
*.bsc
*.sbr
*.ncb
*.idb
